layers.nm: In a galaxy far, far away, hungry travelers found a drive-thru sushi joint called "Sushi Wars: A New Roll." With a towering robot chef and witty Star Wars puns like "May the rolls be with you," customers enjoyed fresh and delicious sushi on the go.
